{
  "stem": "1721.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 93.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he immediately had ordered me taken away, sent to the local hospital for treatment.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And whatever treatment they had at that point-- I don't know if they even had any vaccination.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they actually isolated me in a-- in a hospital unit, and I was able to recuperate there for about a week.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This gave my mother a chance to go back to the apartment, straighten out whatever affairs-- I think she was able to pack some-- some of her personal belongings.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She may be able hide a few things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she did visit me once or twice in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I must have been there a week, maybe 10 days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then when I recuperated from jaundice, then we were then shipped out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We went to another one of these things with the train stations.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That is, I don't remember that time frame very well.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "At that point, we may have been loaded onto the-- to the trains almost immediately, I think.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I found out a lot of years later-- in fact, it was my mother who told me, probably only a few years later that that German officer who had separated me out from the rest and ordered me to the hospital was Adolf Eichmann.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was at that point-- he was in charge of that-- that was his job at that time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was gathering all of the people in Germany for-- for transporting.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He-- well, I don't know if he showed me kindness.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe he didn't want an epidemic right there in the heart of Germany, in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Because we were headed for Thereseinstadt.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
